{"tid":52170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"取西經絕無意義","createTime":"2016-12-23T22:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T22:54:33.000Z","uid":56738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3f40ee82bea728fca0881d5a69110cc4e1270f","tid":52170,"uid":56738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T22:32:57.000Z","msg":"一直都好鐘意之前多位巴打改既呢份詞 今日同大家再回味多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原link <a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=5159771&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DEP%26message%3D5159771%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=blCoIAICFQIi7UBPh56t%2F0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=490ba8ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=5159771&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n歌 <a href=\"https://app.box.com/s/aqldtao47abnql4hsvvi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.box.com%2Fs%2Faqldtao47abnql4hsvvi&d=blCoIAICFQIi7UBPh56t%2F0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=e1ac529d\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.box.com/s/aqldtao47abnql4hsvvi</a><br />\n取西經絕無意義 他不會扭轉沙僧的心意 <br />\n被褫奪身份只有貪嗔癡 <br />\n<br />\n金剛圈亦無意義　今天這緊箍&amp;#22095;足七次 <br />\n又再讓這刺痛一再開始 <br />\n<br />\n＊到底得幾多妖精幾多仙　經書裡佛法也不再有意思 <br />\n　誰對我說過取西經的構思 <br />\n　到底得幾多妖精幾多仙　但為何欠缺了我都不可以 <br />\n　而每個也說要將我　烹煮晚宴　啊！ <br />\n<br />\n＃豬頭悟能出現　花名八戒早已知 <br />\n　捱到這夜方夠腳　齊遠去雷音寺 <br />\n　但日夜面對妖魔千次　放棄原來更易 <br />\n　面對挫敗千百遍　誰笑說不介意？"},{"pid":"62cf37b08a2860606e04fe3ac4011b47067bf534","tid":52170,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T22:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}